data.description:
Step into your future home and receive a remarkable $10,000 credit at closing, providing you with even greater flexibility to manage your closing costs or secure a lower interest rate. 
As you explore your new residence, you'll discover a multitude of features tailored to elevate your lifestyle and contribute to long-term savings:
Lower Bills: Embrace eco-friendly living with solar panels that efficiently trim your energy bills and reduce your carbon footprint.
Year-Round Comfort: Bid farewell to extreme temperatures with a recently installed HVAC system that keeps your home cozy throughout every season.
Instant Hot Water: Enjoy on-demand hot water while saving energy, thanks to the solar hybrid water heater.
Pristine Water: Revel in the purity of soft water throughout your home, a small change with a significant impact on your daily life.
Sun-Filled Relaxation: The patio has been transformed into a year-round sunroom, offering a bright and inviting space to relax and entertain, rain or shine.
Stylish Kitchen: An updated kitchen backsplash adds a contemporary touch to this highly functional space, making cooking and entertaining a delight.
Modern Hardwood: Experience the perfect blend of modern living and easy maintenance with new hardwood flooring that exudes style.
Room for Everything: A spacious 3-car garage provides ample storage for vehicles, tools, and more, ensuring convenience at its finest.
Step outside onto the outdoor wood deck, perfect for gatherings and enjoying the picturesque surroundings. Nestled in a highly desirable neighborhood, this home positions you closer to schools, parks, shopping, and dining. Your dream home isn't just about comfort; it's about elevating your lifestyle while maximizing your savings. Make your move before December 31st to secure the added benefit of the Florida homestead exemption from the start of the New Year.  Includes 1 year Home Warranty w/Choice Home Warranty.
